From c250c238f0852c5c6571dc84c6545b71c43db050 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: LibreELEC <patches@libreelec.tv>
Date: Thu, 25 Jun 2026 12:50:19 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] podman-bin 6.0.0: redirect addon storage paths

Redirect hardcoded upstream paths to LibreELEC addon storage locations
so podman-bin 6.0.0 works correctly within the LibreELEC addon filesystem.

Source: podman-bin-6.0.0.tar.gz
Generated by: tools/podman-bin/gen-patches.sh
Generated on: 2026-06-25 12:50:19 UTC
Generator: git version 2.53.0

Path substitutions applied to all *.go files (non-comment lines only):
  /etc/containers           -> /storage/.kodi/addons/service.system.podman/etc/containers
  /usr/local/etc/containers -> /storage/.kodi/addons/service.system.podman/etc/containers
  /usr/share/containers     -> /storage/.kodi/userdata/addon_data/service.system.podman/podman/etc/containers
  /var/lib/containers       -> /storage/.kodi/userdata/addon_data/service.system.podman/podman

To regenerate this patch after a version bump, update PKG_VERSION in
package.mk and re-run:
  tools/podman-bin/gen-patches.sh

Note: the script skips writing the patch file if the generated content
is identical to the existing patch (ignoring commit hash and timestamps),
avoiding unnecessary commits when the source version has not changed.
